title: Spoing v1.0.4
description:
Diamonds are a Spoing's best friend.

Spoing's colorful rainbow diamonds have been stolen! Now it's up to you to guide him through 50 underground caves to get them back. 

Build platforms using green gems to climb to high up places and throw yourself around in this elastic platform puzzler!

Spoing Highlights:

- Fifty diverse caverns to explore!
- Unique and gorgeous artistic style
- Intuitive flick-and-fling, one touch controls
- Variety of enemies to get in your way
- Set the mood by choosing your own music!

What's New:

Bugfix Level 19
